metadata.title: Herring Catch Landings (Canada)
metadata.description:
Parameter
Herring catch landings recorded from fish slips

Measurement Details
Fish slips are submitted to DFO with each vesselï¾’s landing.  Catch (tonnes) recorded by geographic location, disposal, date, and gear type.

Geographic Area
Canadian Pacific Coast

Other Comments
this web site offers summary catch/landings data in tabular and graphical form for the period 1951-1993

( http://www.pac.dfo.ca/ )  ( http://www.pac.dfo.ca/ops/sa/pages/93grafs.htm )
